OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777539989
OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FThe government has announced that a
OL,7,Ffurther #25 million will be invested
OL,8,Fto increase police patrols and
OL,9,Fsecurity to keep Jewish communities
OL,10,Fsafe after an anti-semitic attack in
OL,11,Fnorth London.
OL,13,FIt comes as the government faces
OL,14,Fmounting pressure to tackle
OL,15,Fantisemitism in the UK following the
OL,16,Fsuspected terror attack in Golders
OL,17,FGreen on Wednesday, in which two
OL,18,FJewish people were stabbed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777539989
OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FIt also said legislation will be fast-
OL,7,Ftracked in the coming weeks to target
OL,8,Fthose acting on behalf of state-
OL,9,Fsponsored groups.
OL,11,FPolice across the country have stepped
OL,12,Fup patrols in response to the attack
OL,13,Fthat saw two Jewish men ` 34-year-old
OL,14,FShilome Rand and 76-year-old Moshe Ben
OL,15,FBaila, named locally as Moshe Shine `
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital after being stabbed
OL,17,Fin Golders Green.
OL,19,FA 45-year-old man, said by police to
OL,20,Fbe a Somali-born British national, was
OL,21,Farrested following the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
