OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777539989
OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FCounter-terrorism officers
OL,7,Finvestigating the attack said they had
OL,8,Fsearched an address in the south-east
OL,9,Fof the city after it was reported the
OL,10,Fsuspect had been involved in a prior
OL,11,F"altercation" with another person.
OL,13,FThe Met said officers were called to
OL,14,Fan address in Great Dover Street,
OL,15,FSouthwark, at around 8.50 am, after a
OL,16,Fsuspect armed with a knife is believed
OL,17,Fto have had an altercation with the
OL,18,Foccupant before leaving.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
