OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FThe occupant suffered minor injuries,
OL,7,Fbut the suspect was not found and
OL,8,Fofficers believe he is the same man
OL,9,Farrested in Golders Green.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV News on Wednesday,
OL,12,FRand said he blamed the government for
OL,13,F"not doing its job" to protect the
OL,14,FJewish community.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
