OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FHe told ITV News UK Editor Paul Brand:
OL,7,F"People are really concerned, people
OL,8,Fare afraid, people are uncomfortable
OL,9,Fwalking in the street, people are
OL,10,Fblaming obviously the government for
OL,11,Fnot doing anything about what's going
OL,12,Fon."
OL,14,FChief Rabbi Sir Ephraim Mirvis called
OL,15,Ffor "meaningful action" to tackle the
OL,16,F"root causes" of antisemitism, while
OL,17,Fthe Board of Deputies of British Jews
OL,18,Fsaid antisemitism must be "confronted,
OL,19,Fpunished and deterred with the full
OL,20,Fforce of the state".
