OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FFootage of the attack posted online
OL,7,Fappears to show a man waiting at a bus
OL,8,Fstop putting on a kippah before an
OL,9,Fattacker lunges at him.
OL,11,FAnother clip shows two police officers
OL,12,Ffacing down the knife-wielding man in
OL,13,Fthe middle of the road, before using a
OL,14,FTaser and kicking him repeatedly in
OL,15,Fthe head.
OL,17,FBody-worn footage released by the
OL,18,FMetropolitan Police shows the moment
OL,19,Ftheir officers came face to face with
OL,20,Fthe suspect, who could be seen walking
OL,21,Ftowards them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
