OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FAbove: Suspect lunges at a man in the
OL,7,Fstreet who manages to escape
OL,9,FThe officers could be heard shouting
OL,10,F"get down on the ground" before
OL,11,Ftasering the man and grappling with
OL,12,Fhim as they could be heard to shout
OL,13,Frepeatedly "drop the knife".
OL,15,FA member of the public could also be
OL,16,Fseen intervening to help apprehend the
OL,17,Fsuspect.
OL,19,F"The suspect refused to show his
OL,20,Fhands, was violent and continued to
OL,21,Fpose a clear threat," the force said.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@XO]uD@LOUuD@[O]{D@AOU}D@UO]
