OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FBritain's most senior police officer,
OL,7,FSir Mark Rowley, said that the suspect
OL,8,Fhas a history of serious violence and
OL,9,Fmental health problems.
OL,11,FAbove: Moment the suspect is tasered
OL,12,Fby police in north London
OL,14,FResponding to the attack, Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer vowed to tackle "malign state
OL,16,Factors" linked to recent violence and
OL,17,Fhas promised to visit Golders Green
OL,18,F"as soon as possible".
OL,26,@wD@YOUxD@GO]zD@AOUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
