OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FOn Thursday, the government announced
OL,7,Flegislation will also be fast-tracked
OL,8,Fin the coming weeks to provide
OL,9,Fauthorities with powers to target
OL,10,Findividuals and groups acting on
OL,11,Fbehalf of state-sponsored
OL,12,Forganisations, following a number of
OL,13,Fincidents linked to Iranian proxies.
OL,15,FIt means anyone acting as a proxy of a
OL,16,Fstate-sponsored group can be
OL,17,Finvestigated and prosecuted under the
OL,18,FNational Security Act, treating them
OL,19,Fin the same way as a foreign
OL,20,Fintelligence operative.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
