OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FBut the prime minister will face
OL,7,Fpressure to go further, including
OL,8,Fcalls to ban pro-Palestinian marches.
OL,10,FJonathan Hall, the former independent
OL,11,Freviewer of terrorism legislation,
OL,12,Fsaid it was currently "impossible" for
OL,13,Fsuch marches not to "incubate"
OL,14,Fantisemitism.
OL,16,FDescribing recent attacks on Jews as a
OL,17,F"massive national security emergency",
OL,18,Fhe called for a "moratorium" on pro-
OL,19,FPalestinian marches.
