OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FOpposition politicians have also
OL,7,Fjoined calls to ban the marches, with
OL,8,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,9,Fsaying it was "quite clear they are
OL,10,Fused as a cover for violence and
OL,11,Fintimidation against Jews".
OL,13,FMeanwhile, police forces across the
OL,14,Fcountry said they would step up
OL,15,Fpatrols in Jewish areas in response to
OL,16,FWednesday's attack.
OL,26,@qD@OOUsD@ZO]
