OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police said it had
OL,7,Fdeployed extra officers around the
OL,8,Fcity, with a "high-visibility presence
OL,9,Fwithin our Jewish communities in north
OL,10,FManchester, Bury and Salford".
OL,12,FWest Yorkshire Police and Thames
OL,13,FValley Police both said they would
OL,14,Fincrease patrols to "provide
OL,15,Fadditional reassurance".
OL,26,@pD@NOUrD@]O]vD@UOUwD@WO]
