OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FFigures covering the 12 months of
OL,7,F2025, published earlier this year by
OL,8,Fthe Community Security Trust (CST),
OL,9,Fconcluded the second-highest annual
OL,10,Ftotal ever recorded for anti-Jewish
OL,11,Fhate incidents, at 3,700, up 4% on the
OL,12,F3,556 incidents recorded in 2024.
OL,14,FThe report noted that dozens of
OL,15,Fantisemitic incidents were reported in
OL,16,Fthe aftermath of the deadly Manchester
OL,17,Fsynagogue attack, some celebrating
OL,18,Fwhat had happened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
