OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777539989
OL,3,CExtra #25m announced to protect Jewish
OL,4,Ccommunities after Golders Green attack
OL,6,FWorshippers Melvin Cravitz and Adrian
OL,7,FDaulby were killed when 35-year-old
OL,8,FJihad Al-Shamie, a Syrian-born British
OL,9,Fcitizen, drove into the gates of the
OL,10,FHeaton Park synagogue in Crumpsall,
OL,11,FManchester, in October last year, and
OL,12,Fthen began attacking with a knife,
OL,13,Fwearing a fake suicide belt.
OL,15,FIt was the first fatal antisemitic
OL,16,Fterror attack in the UK since the CST
OL,17,Fbegan recording incidents in 1984.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
